#: src/ops/cost-tracking.md
msgid "**Background refresh, never blocks.** A single task refreshes a process-wide price snapshot hourly. The cost-recording path reads the cached snapshot synchronously and never makes a network call inline, so a slow gateway can't stall request accounting."
