msgid "**Data dir:** `/zeroclaw-data` (config: `/zeroclaw-data/.zeroclaw/config.toml`, workspace: `/zeroclaw-data/workspace`). Mount a named volume or bind here for persistence; note this is **not** `/root/.zeroclaw`."
msgstr "**数据目录：** `/zeroclaw-data`（配置：`/zeroclaw-data/.zeroclaw/config.toml`，工作区：`/zeroclaw-data/workspace`）。在此处挂载命名卷或绑定卷以实现持久化；请注意，这**不是** `/root/.zeroclaw`。"

