#: src/channels/mattermost.md
msgid "**Isolation is the point.** Each thread's context is self-contained: it does not leak outside the thread, and nothing from outside the thread leaks in. Parallel threads hold separate conversational state, so unrelated tasks never contaminate each other."
msgstr "**隔离正是关键所在。** 每个线程的上下文都是自包含的：它不会泄漏到线程之外，线程之外的任何内容也不会泄漏进来。并行线程持有各自独立的对话状态，因此互不相关的任务永远不会相互干扰。"

#: src/channels/git.md
msgid "**Issue-scoped conversations.** Every message on the same issue or PR shares one conversation thread; the agent replies as a comment on that issue."
msgstr "**问题范围内的对话。** 同一 issue 或 PR 上的每条消息共享一个对话线程；代理作为该 issue 上的评论进行回复。"

#: src/channels/git-github-app.md
