#: src/setup/freebsd.md
msgid "**Repeated `start` stacks orphan supervisors.** A plain `start` does not check whether a supervisor is already running, so a second `start` (or a `start` after a crash that left a stale pidfile) launches another `daemon` that fights the first over the gateway port. Make `start` idempotent by refusing when a live supervisor already exists. Match the supervisor by the launcher path, **not** the pidfile alone (the pidfile can be stale). Two FreeBSD-specific traps when you do this:"
msgstr "**重复执行 `start` 会堆积孤儿监管进程。** 普通的 `start` 不会检查监管进程是否已在运行，因此第二次 `start`（或在崩溃后遗留了过期 pidfile 时执行的 `start`）会启动另一个 `daemon`，与第一个争夺网关端口。应让 `start` 具备幂等性，当已存在活跃的监管进程时拒绝启动。通过启动器路径来匹配监管进程，**而非**仅凭 pidfile（pidfile 可能已过期）。执行此操作时有两个 FreeBSD 特有的陷阱："

