#: src/agents/filesystem.md
msgid "**`shared/`** holds resources agents draw on in common, notably skill bundles under `shared/skills/<bundle>/`."
msgstr "**`shared/`** 存放各 agent 共用的资源，主要是位于 `shared/skills/<bundle>/` 下的技能包。"

#: src/channels/git.md
msgid "**`sop` routing.** A `sop` route emits a channel-sourced SOP event with topic `git.<alias>:<event_type>` and a structured JSON payload. The routed event is consumed by SOP ingress rather than delivered as chat. Match it from `SOP.toml` with a `channel` trigger whose topic is the Git event topic, for example `git.main:pull_request.opened`; use an optional condition such as `$.repo == \"octo/repo\"` to narrow the SOP to one repository."
msgstr "**`sop` 路由。** `sop` 路由会发出一个来源于 channel 的 SOP 事件，其主题为 `git.<alias>:<event_type>`，并带有结构化 JSON 负载。路由后的事件由 SOP ingress 消费，而不是作为聊天消息投递。请在 `SOP.toml` 中使用 `channel` 触发器将其匹配，触发器的 topic 为 Git 事件主题，例如 `git.main:pull_request.opened`；可使用可选条件（如 `$.repo == \"octo/repo\"`）将 SOP 限定到单个仓库。"

#: src/agents/delegation.md
msgid "**`spawn_subagent`**: runs the SAME agent again under its own identity for a focused subtask. The child sees the parent's full permissions envelope minus any narrowing. Use when the parent wants to scope an internal subtask out of its main conversation history without changing identity."
msgstr "**`spawn_subagent`**：在其自身身份下再次运行同一个 agent，以执行一个聚焦的子任务。子 agent 会继承父 agent 的完整权限范围，但可能会有所收窄。当父 agent 希望将某个内部子任务从其主对话历史中独立出来，而不改变身份时，可使用此功能。"

#: src/plugins/writing-a-tool-plugin.md
msgid "**`success: false` versus `Err`.** A `ToolResult` with `success: false` flows back to the model as a normal tool response it can react to (retry with fixed arguments, apologize, pick another tool). An `Err(String)` crosses the boundary as a plugin fault: the host wraps it as `plugin execute returned error` and the call fails. Reserve `Err` for genuinely broken states, and report bad input via `success: false`."
msgstr "**`success: false` 与 `Err`。** `success: false` 的 `ToolResult` 会作为普通工具响应返回给模型，模型可以据此作出反应（使用修正后的参数重试、道歉、选择另一个工具）。`Err(String)` 会作为插件故障跨越边界：宿主会将其包装为 `plugin execute returned error`，并使调用失败。请将 `Err` 保留给真正损坏的状态，并通过 `success: false` 报告错误输入。"

#: src/providers/streaming.md
msgid "**`supports_streaming_tool_events`**: true when the provider emits `ToolCall` events during the stream rather than at the end"
msgstr "**`supports_streaming_tool_events`**：当提供方在流式传输过程中（而非结束时）发出 `ToolCall` 事件时为 true"

#: src/providers/streaming.md
msgid "**`supports_streaming`**: true for every actively maintained provider"
msgstr "**`supports_streaming`**：对于每个积极维护的提供商均为 true"

#: src/zerocode/themes.md
msgid "**`terminal`**: inherits your terminal's own colors. Every role is left to the terminal default and the app skips painting a background, so a tuned shell palette shows through untouched."
msgstr "**`terminal`**：继承终端自身的颜色。每个角色都保留终端默认值，应用不会绘制背景，因此经过调校的 shell 调色板可以原样显示。"

