#: src/agents/overview.md
msgid "A [SubAgent](./delegation.md) is the short-lived exception to coexistence: an agent can spawn an ephemeral SubAgent that inherits the parent's identity and security policy for a single task. See [Delegation & SubAgents](./delegation.md)."
msgstr "[SubAgent](./delegation.md) 是共存机制中短暂存在的例外：一个 agent 可以派生出一个临时的 SubAgent，该 SubAgent 会继承父 agent 的身份和安全策略，以执行单个任务。参见[委派与 SubAgent](./delegation.md)。"

#: src/setup/freebsd.md
msgid "A `\"status\":\"ok\"` health payload means the gateway is up; the response's `runtime` field carries the per-component health (channels, providers, and so on)."
msgstr "`\"status\":\"ok\"` 健康检查负载表示网关已正常运行；响应的 `runtime` 字段携带各组件的健康状况（通道、提供方等等）。"

