msgid "A dev box where you're iterating fast and approval prompts slow you down"
msgstr "一个开发环境，你在其中快速迭代，而审批提示会拖慢你的进度"

#: src/channels/peer-groups.md
msgid "A discord peer group named e.g. `my_discord_group` sets `channel = \"discord\"`, allows `111111111111111111` in `external_peers`, names peer agents researcher, summariser, and blocks `222222222222222222` via `ignore`. Set it through the gateway dashboard, zerocode, or `zeroclaw config set`."
msgstr "一个名为例如 `my_discord_group` 的 discord 对等组设置 `channel = \"discord\"`，在 `external_peers` 中允许 `111111111111111111`，将对等代理命名为 researcher、summariser，并通过 `ignore` 屏蔽 `222222222222222222`。可通过网关仪表板、zerocode 或 `zeroclaw config set` 进行设置。"

