#: src/channels/amqp.md
msgid "Acknowledgement mode. When `true` (default), deliveries are acked only after the message is durably handed to the agent loop, giving at-least-once semantics: a crash before hand-off redelivers the event. Set `false` for at-most-once (broker acks on dispatch), which silently drops in-flight events on crash and is only appropriate for non-side-effecting, drop-on-overload consumers."
msgstr "确认模式。为 `true`（默认）时，只有在消息已持久化交给 agent 循环后才会确认投递，从而提供至少一次语义：在交接前崩溃会重新投递该事件。将其设为 `false` 可实现至多一次（broker 在分发时确认），这会在崩溃时静默丢弃飞行中的事件，仅适用于不会产生副作用、在过载时可丢弃的消费者。"

