#: src/maintainers/reviewer-playbook.md
msgid "At the follow-up date, re-check live state. If the author responded or the branch became reviewable, remove or keep off `stale-candidate`. If there is still no response and no maintainer takeover or replacement path, close with a backlog-hygiene rationale and a clear reopening or replacement path."
msgstr "在跟进日期，重新检查实时状态。如果作者已回复，或者该分支已变为可审查，则移除或继续保持 `stale-candidate` 不开启。如果仍无回复，且没有维护者接手或替代路径，则以 backlog 清理为由关闭，并提供明确的重新开启或替代路径。"

#: src/architecture/memory-payload-lifecycle.md
msgid "At turn start, the runtime can recall relevant memories and inject a bounded `[Memory context]` block into the user-visible prompt context. Related entry points do not all apply identical filters. The channel/interactive loop filters generated autosave noise, stale `<tool_result>` blocks, and Conversation entries when the turn has no safe session scope or is not user-initiated. Generic memory loading filters autosave noise and relevance, but does not by itself enforce that channel-loop Conversation exclusion."
msgstr "在回合开始时，运行时可以回忆相关记忆，并将一个有界的 `[Memory context]` 块注入到用户可见的提示上下文中。相关入口点并不都应用相同的过滤器。通道/交互循环会在该回合没有安全的会话作用域或不是用户发起时，过滤生成的自动保存噪声、过期的 `<tool_result>` 块以及 Conversation 条目。通用记忆加载会过滤自动保存噪声和相关性，但其本身并不强制执行通道循环的 Conversation 排除。"

