msgid "Both panes drive a specific agent, and zerocode can give each agent its own colour palette so you can tell them apart at a glance, see [Per-agent themes](../zerocode/themes.md#per-agent-themes-code--chat-panes). The **Config** pane is the preferred place to add and wire agents without editing files by hand."
msgstr "两个窗格各自驱动一个特定的智能体，zerocode 可以为每个智能体设置专属的配色方案，让你一眼就能区分它们，详见 [按智能体主题](../zerocode/themes.md#per-agent-themes-code--chat-panes)。**Config** 窗格是添加和连接智能体的首选位置，无需手动编辑文件。"

