#: src/channels/mattermost.md
msgid "Channel IDs to restrict the bot to. Empty or `[\"*\"]` = auto-discover every channel the bot can read (public, private, DMs, group DMs) and poll them all. Explicit IDs disable discovery and pin the bot to the listed channels only. Migrated from the legacy `channel_id` singular field."
msgstr "用于限制机器人的频道 ID。留空或 `[\"*\"]` = 自动发现机器人可读取的每个频道（公开、私密、私信、群组私信）并轮询所有频道。指定明确的 ID 将禁用自动发现，并将机器人锁定到列出的频道。从旧版 `channel_id` 单数字段迁移而来。"

#: src/channels/discord.md
msgid "Channel IDs to watch. Empty = watch every channel the bot can see. Used by the archive sidecar (when `archive = true`) and by the in-channel filter when set."
msgstr "要监视的频道 ID。留空 = 监视机器人可见的每个频道。由归档附属程序（当 `archive = true` 时）使用，并在设置后由频道内过滤器使用。"

