msgid "Cloud API via Kilo AI Gateway. Bearer-token auth with multiple model tiers (free, balanced, pro). The `/models` endpoint is public (`PUBLIC_MODEL_LISTING`), so model listing works without a credential. Because it is queried live, it is the source that carries pricing into the cost-rates editor. The shared models.dev catalog (`kilo` key) is only a fallback for when the live endpoint is unreachable, and it does not include pricing."
