msgstr "保存能否在进程重新加载后仍然保留，而不仅仅是立即的内存中渲染？"

#: src/architecture/tool-execution-lifecycle.md
msgid "Does cancellation close only unfinished tool cards/results?"
msgstr "取消只会关闭未完成的工具卡片/结果吗？"

#: src/architecture/channel-runtime-lifecycle.md
msgid "Does fast acknowledgement, if any, still preserve the same background turn behavior as synchronous dispatch?"
msgstr "快速确认（如果有）是否仍会保留与同步分发相同的后台轮换行为？"

#: src/architecture/tool-execution-lifecycle.md
msgid "Does non-interactive execution deny or use a real backchannel rather than silently approving?"
msgstr "非交互式执行会拒绝，还是会使用真实的回传通道，而不是静默批准？"

#: src/maintainers/pr-workflow.md
msgid "Does not mean"
msgstr "并不意味着"

#: src/foundations/fnd-003-governance.md
msgid "Does not own"
msgstr "不拥有"

#: src/architecture/tool-execution-lifecycle.md
