#: src/architecture/decisions/ADR-003-wasm-plugin-model.md
msgid "Each plugin shipped a `manifest.toml` alongside its `.wasm` file. The manifest declared name, version, capabilities such as `tool`, `channel`, `memory`, and `observer`, and required permissions such as `http_client`, `env_read`, `file_read`, `file_write`, `memory_read`, and `memory_write`."
msgstr "每个插件都随其 `.wasm` 文件一起提供了一个 `manifest.toml`。该清单声明了名称、版本、功能（如 `tool`、`channel`、`memory` 和 `observer`），以及所需权限（如 `http_client`、`env_read`、`file_read`、`file_write`、`memory_read` 和 `memory_write`）。"

