#: src/maintainers/release-runbook.md
msgid "Everything else, a `tsc` error, a missing file, a Rust compile failure, a `cargo` lockfile mismatch, is a real defect. Do not click **Run workflow** on the GitHub Actions form until those are fixed via a standard PR off master."
