#: src/maintainers/labels.md
msgid "Explicit stale exemption for accepted or otherwise long-lived work that is not already protected by another stale exclusion. Target policy: use only when the [Project board contract](./pr-workflow.md#issue-routing-evidence) has a contributor-visible stale-exemption reason and routing evidence. Active release trackers and active RFC or design trackers may use the tracker itself as the visible reason and routing surface while they remain active; revisit them when the milestone closes, the tracker drifts from live state, the RFC reaches a decision, is superseded, or closes, or the issue stops representing an active project decision surface. Existing exemptions missing those facts should be audited and repaired before stale sweeps stop honoring them."
msgstr "针对已接受或其他长期存在的工作的显式过期豁免，前提是这些工作尚未受到其他过期排除规则的保护。目标策略：仅当[项目看板约定](./pr-workflow.md#issue-routing-evidence)具有贡献者可见的过期豁免原因和路由证据时才使用。处于活动状态的发布跟踪器以及活动的 RFC 或设计跟踪器，在其保持活动状态期间，可将跟踪器本身用作可见原因和路由载体；当里程碑关闭、跟踪器偏离实时状态、RFC 达成决议、被取代或关闭，或该 issue 不再代表活动的项目决策载体时，应重新审视它们。对于缺失上述事实的现有豁免，应在过期清理停止承认它们之前进行审计和修复。"

