#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md
msgid "For providers that frequently encounter rate limits, supply additional API keys on the provider entry that ZeroClaw rotates through on `429` responses. The primary `api_key` is always tried first; extras are rotated on rate-limit errors. All keys must belong to the same provider account class; this is rate-limit smoothing, not multi-tenant key juggling."
msgstr "对于经常遇到速率限制的提供商，可以在提供商条目中提供额外的 API 密钥，ZeroClaw 会在收到 `429` 响应时轮换使用这些密钥。主 `api_key` 始终最先尝试；额外的密钥会在出现速率限制错误时轮换使用。所有密钥必须属于同一提供商账户类别；这只是为了平滑速率限制，而不是多租户密钥管理。"

#: src/maintainers/docs-and-translations.md
