#: src/agents/anatomy.md
msgid "Initialize this agent's `mcp_bundles` tools when it serves an ACP (`session/new`) session. Off by default: MCP servers are external processes/services that can block startup while they connect, and ACP `session/new` is expected to return promptly. Enable it when this agent must call its `mcp_bundles` tools over ACP; `session/new` then pays the one-time MCP connection cost (bounded and non-fatal per server). Set per agent so each ACP profile opts in independently; when this agent is the ACP default (`acp.default_agent`, or the sole configured agent), the flag is picked up automatically for sessions that omit `agentAlias`."
msgstr "当该 agent 提供 ACP (`session/new`) 会话时，初始化其 `mcp_bundles` 工具。默认关闭：MCP 服务器是外部进程/服务，在连接时可能阻塞启动，而 ACP `session/new` 预期应尽快返回。仅当该 agent 必须通过 ACP 调用其 `mcp_bundles` 工具时启用；这样 `session/new` 会承担一次性的 MCP 连接成本（每个服务器都有上限且非致命）。按 agent 单独设置，这样每个 ACP 配置文件都可独立选择加入；当该 agent 是 ACP 默认值（`acp.default_agent`，或是唯一配置的 agent）时，对于省略 `agentAlias` 的会话会自动采用该标志。"

