#: src/tools/mcp.md
msgid "Load MCP tool schemas on-demand via `tool_search` instead of eagerly including them in the LLM context window. When enabled, only tool names are listed in the system prompt; the LLM must call `tool_search` to fetch full schemas before invoking a deferred tool."
