#: src/sop/fan-in/channel.md
msgid "Load a SOP with a `channel` trigger, then send a message to that channel. The `channel` trigger is the opt-in: the orchestrator only lifts inbound messages into events when a loaded SOP wants channel events. It puts the channel kind and alias into the topic and the content into the payload, then dispatches it. A run starts for every loaded SOP whose `channel` (and `alias`, if set) matches and whose `condition` (if any) holds against the content. The normal agent turn still runs alongside any run that starts."
msgstr "加载一个带有 `channel` 触发器的 SOP，然后向该 channel 发送一条消息。`channel` 触发器是一个可选订阅机制：只有当已加载的 SOP 需要 channel 事件时，编排器才会把传入消息提升为事件。它会将 channel 类型和别名放入 topic，并将内容放入 payload，然后分发它。对于每个已加载的 SOP，只要其 `channel`（以及如果已设置的 `alias`）匹配，并且其 `condition`（如果有）针对内容成立，就会启动一次 run。正常的 agent turn 仍会与任何已启动的 run 并行执行。"

