#: src/setup/linux.md
msgid "Neither works yet. `cargo binstall zeroclaw` resolves crate metadata from crates.io, but ZeroClaw is not published there (`publish = false`), so there is nothing for it to fetch; `nix run github:zeroclaw-labs/zeroclaw` does not launch the agent because the flake exposes only a dev toolchain, not a runnable package ([\\#5987](https://github.com/zeroclaw-labs/zeroclaw/issues/5987)). `install.sh` already does what `binstall` would (download a prebuilt release binary), so it remains the supported one-liner."
msgstr "目前两者都尚未生效。`cargo binstall zeroclaw` 会从 crates.io 解析 crate 元数据，但 ZeroClaw 并未发布到那里（`publish = false`），因此没有任何内容可供其拉取；`nix run github:zeroclaw-labs/zeroclaw` 也无法启动该 agent，因为该 flake 仅暴露了开发工具链，而非可运行的软件包（[\\#5987](https://github.com/zeroclaw-labs/zeroclaw/issues/5987)）。`install.sh` 已经实现了 `binstall` 本应完成的工作（下载预构建的发行版二进制文件），因此它仍然是受支持的一行命令安装方式。"

