#: src/maintainers/release-runbook.md
msgid "Open a PR. Label it `type:ci`, `size:XS`, and any path labels the PR labeler adds. If the PR raises a toolchain floor, also apply `risk:high` and route it through lane D. Get one maintainer review. Merge when CI is green. The **Installer Drift** gate in CI fails the PR if a generated surface is out of sync with the spec, so a missed regeneration cannot land. The **Validate Translations Pin** gate resolves the submodule at the pinned commit and validates catalogue format and msgid parity, so a bad pin cannot land either. See [Docs & Translations](../maintainers/docs-and-translations.md) for catalogue refresh details."
msgstr "打开一个 PR。给它添加 `type:ci`、`size:XS`，以及 PR 标记器添加的任何路径标签。如果 PR 提高了工具链最低版本，还要添加 `risk:high` 并通过 lane D 路由。获取一位维护者审查。CI 通过后合并。CI 中的 **Installer Drift** gate 会在生成的 surface 与 spec 不一致时使 PR 失败，因此遗漏的重新生成无法落地。**Validate Translations Pin** gate 会在固定的 commit 上解析 submodule，并验证 catalogue 格式和 msgid 一致性，因此错误的 pin 也无法落地。有关 catalogue 刷新详情，请参见 [Docs & Translations](../maintainers/docs-and-translations.md)。"

