#: src/maintainers/ci-and-actions.md
msgid "Runs only when Docker image or release-Docker context files change. It prepares a smoke `docker-ctx` with the same helper used by the stable release workflow, then builds the default prebuilt image and the Debian compatibility prebuilt image from `Dockerfile.ci` without pushing either image. This catches image dependency and `COPY` path breakage before release without giving PR runs registry write permission or running on every PR."
msgstr "仅在 Docker 镜像或 release-Docker 上下文文件发生变更时运行。它使用稳定版发布工作流所用的同一辅助工具准备一个 smoke `docker-ctx`，然后从 `Dockerfile.ci` 构建默认的预构建镜像和 Debian 兼容的预构建镜像，且不推送任何一个镜像。这样可以在发布前捕获镜像依赖和 `COPY` 路径损坏，同时不赋予 PR 运行写入镜像仓库的权限，也不会在每个 PR 上运行。"

