#: src/contributing/architecture-map.md
msgid "Runtime changes often affect multiple user paths and need boundary-level tests. Provider token streaming stays runtime-owned; channel draft or typing-indicator streaming follows the channel lifecycle row. Tool-loop changes should name whether they affect approval, dispatch, receipts, observer events, history, or cancellation."
