msgstr "场景"

#: src/reference/cli.md
msgid "Schedule recurring, one-shot, or interval-based tasks using cron expressions, RFC3339 timestamps with explicit Z or offsets, durations, or fixed intervals."
msgstr "使用 cron 表达式、带有显式 Z 或偏移量的 RFC3339 时间戳、持续时间或固定间隔来安排周期性、一次性或基于间隔的任务。"

