msgid "Storage is a two-tier alias-keyed map: `[storage.<backend>.<alias>]`, parallel to `[providers.models.<type>.<alias>]`. Each backend has its own typed config struct. `MemoryConfig.backend` carries a dotted reference (`\"sqlite.default\"`, `\"postgres.work\"`) that resolves to one of these entries via \\[`Config::resolve_active_storage`\\]."
