#: src/providers/openai-codex-subscription.md
msgid "The `responses` wire API hits the Codex backend directly, so the `model` value must be an **exact served ID**: the Codex CLI's client-side aliases (`gpt-5`, `gpt-5.3`, `instant`, `gpt-5.5-instant`) are not resolved here and fail with a `400`."
