#: src/sop/fan-in/amqp.md
msgid "The `routing_key` uses AMQP topic-exchange semantics: keys are `.`\\-delimited words, `*` matches exactly one word, and `#` matches zero or more words. The delivery body is forwarded into the SOP event payload, available to an optional trigger `condition`; step context receives the capped, sanitized, framed form. A JSON-path `condition` such as `$.value > 85` requires the publisher to send a JSON body."
msgstr "`routing_key` 使用 AMQP 主题交换机语义：键是用 `.`\\-分隔的单词，`*` 精确匹配一个单词，`#` 匹配零个或多个单词。传递的正文会转发到 SOP 事件负载中，供可选的触发器 `condition` 使用；步骤上下文接收的是经过截断、清理和封装后的形式。像 `$.value > 85` 这样的 JSON-path `condition` 要求发布者发送 JSON 正文。"

