#: src/developing/plugin-protocol.md
msgid "The call is fire-and-forget: it returns nothing and the host (`component_logging.rs`) absorbs all errors, so a failed log write can never crash plugin execution. `plugin-action` and `plugin-outcome` mirror the closed `Action` / `EventOutcome` taxonomies in `zeroclaw-log`; there is no escape-hatch variant on purpose. Do not call `wasi:logging` directly, plugin events would be formatted inconsistently and would not reach all of the destinations `zeroclaw_log` writes to."
msgstr "该调用是 fire-and-forget：它不返回任何内容，并且宿主（`component_logging.rs`）会吸收所有错误，因此写日志失败绝不会导致插件执行崩溃。`plugin-action` 和 `plugin-outcome` 反映了 `zeroclaw-log` 中封闭的 `Action` / `EventOutcome` 分类；刻意不提供逃生舱变体。不要直接调用 `wasi:logging`，否则插件事件的格式会不一致，并且不会到达 `zeroclaw_log` 写入的所有目标。"

#: src/agents/delegation.md
