#: src/plugins/writing-a-channel-plugin.md
msgid "The host adapter's unit tests in `wasm_channel.rs` are the executable specification: they cover the configure jail (a plugin without `config_read` receives `{}`, never another channel's secrets), the inbound queue handoff, capability-gated dispatch, and poll-health accounting."
msgstr "`wasm_channel.rs` 中宿主适配器的单元测试就是可执行规范：它们覆盖了配置隔离（没有 `config_read` 的插件接收 `{}`，绝不会收到其他通道的密钥）、入站队列交接、能力门控分发，以及轮询健康状态统计。"

#: src/architecture/decisions/ADR-009-wit-wasmtime-plugin-execution.md
msgid "The host does not expose a raw environment-variable read function."
msgstr "主机不提供原始环境变量读取函数。"

#: src/developing/how-plugins-work.md
msgid "The host grants permissions narrowly: a permission the manifest does not declare is a host function the plugin cannot reach. The HTTP-egress and per-plugin configuration boundaries (SSRF-guarded egress that cannot reach loopback, private, link-local, or cloud-metadata addresses or redirect into one; config injected per-alias so a plugin reads only its own resolved values and never the raw process environment or another plugin's secrets) are delivered by the companion plugin-hardening work and are documented alongside those changes. This page covers the signature-policy boundary."
msgstr "宿主以严格限定的方式授予权限：清单未声明的权限，属于插件无法访问的宿主函数。HTTP-egress 和按插件划分的配置边界（受 SSRF 防护的 egress，无法访问 loopback、私有、link-local 或云元数据地址，也不会重定向到这些地址之一；按别名注入配置，使插件只读取自身解析后的值，绝不读取原始进程环境或其他插件的密钥）由配套的插件加固工作提供，并在这些更改旁边记录。此页面涵盖签名策略边界。"

#: src/developing/plugin-protocol.md
msgid "The host lives in `crates/zeroclaw-plugins/src/component.rs`. It holds one async-enabled `wasmtime::Engine`, generates the world bindings with `wasmtime::component::bindgen!` from `wit/v0`, and wires a sandboxed WASI p2 surface into each world's linker. Per-call host state (`PluginState`) carries a `WasiCtx` built with no preopens and no network, plus the `ResourceTable` WASI requires. The only host import wired into the linker is `logging`; a plugin's ambient authority is therefore the sandboxed WASI context and nothing else (see Host imports)."
msgstr "主机位于 `crates/zeroclaw-plugins/src/component.rs`。它持有一个启用了异步的 `wasmtime::Engine`，通过 `wasmtime::component::bindgen!` 从 `wit/v0` 生成 world 绑定，并将一个受沙箱限制的 WASI p2 接口接入每个 world 的链接器。每次调用的主机状态（`PluginState`）携带一个使用无预打开目录且无网络构建的 `WasiCtx`，以及 WASI 所需的 `ResourceTable`。接入链接器的唯一主机导入是 `logging`；因此，插件的环境权限仅限于受沙箱限制的 WASI 上下文，别无其他（见 Host imports）。"

#: src/plugins/writing-a-channel-plugin.md
