#: src/plugins/distributing-plugins.md
msgid "The install path is the local plugin directory; a registry is only a JSON index consulted at command time (`zeroclaw plugin search` / `install`). The default index is the `zeroclaw-labs/zeroclaw-plugins` repository's `registry.json`; private registries are a URL away (`--registry <url>` per command, or the `ZEROCLAW_PLUGIN_REGISTRY_URL` environment variable, resolved in that order per `registry_url` in `src/plugin_registry.rs`)."
msgstr "安装路径是本地插件目录；注册表只是一个在命令执行时查阅的 JSON 索引（`zeroclaw plugin search` / `install`）。默认索引是 `zeroclaw-labs/zeroclaw-plugins` 仓库的 `registry.json`；私有注册表只需提供一个 URL（每个命令使用 `--registry <url>`，或使用 `ZEROCLAW_PLUGIN_REGISTRY_URL` 环境变量，按 `src/plugin_registry.rs` 中的 `registry_url` 以该顺序解析）。"

