msgid "The seven disciplines in §4 are not requirements to master before you can contribute. They are a map of the territory: things you will encounter as you work, named clearly enough that you know what you are looking at when you see them."
msgstr "§4 中的七项准则并不是你必须先掌握才能参与贡献的前提条件。它们是这片领域的地图：是你在工作过程中会遇到的事物，并被清晰地命名，让你在见到它们时能够明白自己所面对的是什么。"

