#: src/sop/fan-in/channel.md
msgid "The transport side (bot token, allowed users, per-channel behavior) is configured on each [channel](../../channels/overview.md). This page covers the trigger. Agent-loop channels have no per-channel dispatch switch: the SOP's `channel` trigger is the opt-in, and the normal agent turn always runs alongside any SOP run it starts."
msgstr "传输侧（bot token、allowed users、按 channel 的行为）是在每个 [channel](../../channels/overview.md) 上配置的。本页介绍 trigger。agent-loop channels 没有 per-channel dispatch switch：SOP 的 `channel` trigger 就是 opt-in，普通 agent turn 总会与它启动的任何 SOP run 一起运行。"

#: src/sop/fan-in/mqtt.md
msgid "The transport side (broker URL, credentials, TLS, QoS) is configured on the [MQTT channel](../../channels/mqtt.md). This page covers the trigger."
msgstr "传输端（broker URL、凭据、TLS、QoS）在 [MQTT channel](../../channels/mqtt.md) 上配置。此页面介绍触发器。"

#: src/sop/fan-in/amqp.md
msgid "The transport side (broker connection, queue, exchange, TLS) is configured on the [AMQP channel](../../channels/amqp.md). This page covers the trigger. The dispatch mode that decides whether deliveries drive the agent loop, the SOP engine, or both is the channel's `dispatch` field."
msgstr "传输端（broker 连接、队列、交换器、TLS）在 [AMQP channel](../../channels/amqp.md) 上配置。本页面涵盖触发器。决定投递是驱动 agent 循环、SOP 引擎，还是两者兼有的分发模式，是 channel 的 `dispatch` 字段。"

#: src/sop/fan-in/git.md
msgid "The transport side (provider, forge auth, polling, repository scoping, event routes) is configured on the [Git channel](../../channels/git.md). This page covers the trigger. Which event types reach SOP ingress is decided by the channel's per-event `events` route table."
msgstr "传输端（provider、forge auth、polling、repository scoping、event routes）在 [Git channel](../../channels/git.md) 上配置。本页介绍触发器。哪些事件类型会到达 SOP ingress 由 channel 的按事件 `events` 路由表决定。"

#: src/sop/fan-in/filesystem.md
msgid "The transport side (watched paths, include and exclude globs, broad-root and symlink safety) is configured on the [Filesystem channel](../../channels/filesystem.md). This page covers the trigger."
msgstr "传输端（监视路径、包含和排除 glob、宽根目录和符号链接安全）在 [Filesystem channel](../../channels/filesystem.md) 上配置。此页面涵盖触发器。"

