msgid "This is a classification map, not a removal plan. Do not remove or externalize a tool until the replacement preserves the operator contract: config, security policy, tool receipts, audit visibility, compatibility, and rollback."
msgstr "这是一个分类映射，不是移除计划。在替代方案保留操作员契约之前，不要移除或外部化任何工具：配置、安全策略、工具回执、审计可见性、兼容性和回滚。"

#: src/security/model.md
msgid "This is a reasonable middle ground, safe enough for a laptop, permissive enough to not frustrate. Crank it up for production (OTP, audit, restricted tools) or down to [YOLO](../getting-started/yolo.md) for a dev box."
msgstr "这是一个合理的折中方案，对于笔记本电脑来说足够安全，又足够宽松而不会让人感到沮丧。在生产环境中可以调高设置（OTP、审计、受限工具），或者在开发机上调低到 [YOLO](../getting-started/yolo.md)。"

#: src/architecture/decisions/ADR-004-tool-shared-state-ownership.md
