#: src/architecture/decisions/ADR-003-wasm-plugin-model.md
msgid "This is a restored retroactive record. The original ADR was added under `docs/architecture/decisions/adr-003-wasm-extism-plugin-model.md` and was dropped during the mdBook migration. It records the historical Extism-based plugin bridge that was accepted on 2026-03-15. The current WIT and direct `wasmtime` model supersedes it in [ADR-009](./ADR-009-wit-wasmtime-plugin-execution.md)."
