#: src/plugins/index.md
msgid "Tool calls are stateless by construction: `WasmTool::execute` builds a fresh store, runs the call, and drops it. Channels and memory backends are stateful by nature, so they hold one warm store for the plugin's lifetime; the host refuels it before every call so a long-lived plugin gets a full budget per call rather than draining over time."
msgstr "工具调用在结构上是无状态的：`WasmTool::execute` 会构建一个新的 store，运行调用，然后将其丢弃。通道和内存后端本质上是有状态的，因此它们会在插件的整个生命周期内持有一个热 store；宿主会在每次调用前为其重新加注，因此一个长生命周期的插件在每次调用时都能获得完整预算，而不是随着时间推移被逐步耗尽。"

