#: src/channels/chat-others.md
msgid "Use case: paired-identity channels where sub-second replies are an AI-tell. Wire-level coverage exists end-to-end across nine channels (Telegram, Discord, Slack, Mattermost, Webhook, iMessage, Matrix, Signal, WhatsApp); integration tests pin the floor + overflow contract on Telegram and WhatsApp Web."
msgstr "用例：成对身份的通道，其中亚秒级回复是 AI 的破绽。在九个通道（Telegram、Discord、Slack、Mattermost、Webhook、iMessage、Matrix、Signal、WhatsApp）上存在端到端的线级覆盖；集成测试在 Telegram 和 WhatsApp Web 上锁定了下限 + 溢出契约。"

