#: src/developing/index.md
msgid "Use these pages when working with ZeroClaw's plugin system or on project tooling. For step-by-step plugin authoring, see the [Guides](../plugins/index.md)."
msgstr "在使用 ZeroClaw 的插件系统或项目工具时，请使用这些页面。有关分步插件编写，请参阅 [Guides](../plugins/index.md)。"

