msgstr "在将审查权移交其他维护者或代理时，请包含："

#: src/tools/overview.md
msgid "When receipts are enabled, successful executions receive a [tool receipt](../security/tool-receipts.md). Denied, blocked, replaced, failed, or interrupted calls do not receive receipts."
msgstr "启用收据后，成功执行会收到一个 [tool receipt](../security/tool-receipts.md)。被拒绝、阻止、替换、失败或中断的调用不会收到收据。"

#: src/security/tool-receipts.md
msgid "When receipts are enabled, the runtime creates a 256-bit in-memory key for the active receipt scope. Channel-server paths keep that key in `ChannelRuntimeContext`; direct turn paths create a fresh scope for the turn. The key is never written to disk, never sent to the model, and never logged."
msgstr "当启用收据时，运行时会为活动收据作用域创建一个 256 位的内存密钥。Channel-server 路径将该密钥保存在 `ChannelRuntimeContext` 中；direct turn 路径则为该轮创建一个新的作用域。该密钥绝不会写入磁盘，绝不会发送给模型，也绝不会记录到日志中。"

