#: src/reference/cli.md
msgid "With --new, generates a fresh pairing code even if the gateway was previously paired (useful for adding additional clients). This does NOT revoke existing tokens."
msgstr "使用 --new，即使网关之前已配对，也会生成一个新的配对码（用于添加其他客户端时很有用）。这不会撤销现有令牌。"

#: src/reference/cli.md
msgid "With --rotate, revokes ALL paired bearer tokens, clears the device registry, and issues a fresh code. Use this after a suspected token leak when you do not know which token was compromised; every client must re-pair."
msgstr "使用 --rotate 时，会撤销所有已配对的 bearer 令牌，清除设备注册表，并签发一个新代码。当你怀疑令牌泄露但不知道是哪个令牌被泄露时，请在此之后使用；所有客户端都必须重新配对。"

#: src/reference/cli.md
msgid "With --rotate-device ID, revokes just that device's bearer token and issues a fresh code for re-pairing that one device."
msgstr "使用 `--rotate-device ID` 时，只会撤销该设备的 bearer token，并为重新配对该设备发放一个新 code。"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md
msgid "With Ollama, this is a no-text-fallback profile: authorized tools remain configured in `risk_profile`, but text-form tool markup from the model is not executed. Use it for chat-first local agents, or for providers that return native/structured tool calls. If a local model must use ZeroClaw's text fallback tool syntax, set `strict_tool_parsing = false` and keep the other small-model limits."
msgstr "使用 Ollama 时，这是一个无文本回退配置文件：已授权的工具仍在 `risk_profile` 中配置，但模型的文本形式工具标记不会被执行。可将其用于聊天优先的本地智能体，或用于返回原生/结构化工具调用的提供商。如果本地模型必须使用 ZeroClaw 的文本回退工具语法，请设置 `strict_tool_parsing = false` 并保留其他小模型限制。"

#: src/contributing/agent-policy-parity-harness.md
msgid "With `resolve()` in place (see above), each surface PR follows these steps:"
msgstr "有了 `resolve()`（见上文），每个表层 PR 按以下步骤进行："

#: src/sop/fan-in/mqtt.md
msgid "With a SOP loaded and the MQTT channel subscribed, publish a message to a topic the trigger pattern matches (for example with `mosquitto_pub`, or any broker client). The listener builds an event from the topic and payload and dispatches it. A run starts for every loaded SOP whose `topic` pattern matches and whose `condition` (if any) holds against the payload."
msgstr "在加载了 SOP 且订阅了 MQTT 频道后，将消息发布到触发器模式匹配的主题（例如使用 `mosquitto_pub`，或任何 broker 客户端）。监听器会根据主题和有效载荷构建事件并分发它。对于每个已加载且其 `topic` 模式匹配、并且其 `condition`（如有）对有效载荷成立的 SOP，都会启动一次运行。"

#: src/sop/fan-in/filesystem.md
msgid "With a SOP loaded and the filesystem channel watching a path, write to that path to produce a change the watcher delivers: create, modify, rename, or delete a file inside a watched root. The watcher debounces and settles the change, then dispatches it. A run starts for every loaded SOP whose `path` glob and `events` filter match, and whose `condition` (if any) holds against the change payload."
msgstr "在已加载 SOP 且文件系统通道正在监视某个路径时，向该路径写入内容以产生一个 watcher 会送达的变更：在受监视的根目录中创建、修改、重命名或删除一个文件。watcher 会对变更进行去抖并等待稳定，然后再派发。对于每个已加载的 SOP，只要其 `path` glob 和 `events` 过滤器匹配，并且其 `condition`（如果有）针对变更负载成立，就会启动一次运行。"

#: src/reference/cli.md
msgid "With no subcommand, prints the catalog of supported provider types. With `create`/`list`/`rename`/`delete`, manages configured provider aliases under `[providers.<category>.<family>.<alias>]`."
msgstr "不带子命令时，打印受支持的提供程序类型目录。使用 `create`/`list`/`rename`/`delete` 时，管理 `[providers.<category>.<family>.<alias>]` 下已配置的提供程序别名。"

#: src/security/tool-receipts.md
msgid "With receipts"
msgstr "带有收据"

#: src/tools/skills.md
msgid "With reflection enabled, ZeroClaw instead asks the agent's configured model provider to synthesize a canonical [`SKILL.md`](#create-a-markdown-skill) from a **bounded** slice of the execution (the task, the tool-call trace, and the final answer). Every input is independently truncated to a configured character budget so a large execution can never produce an unbounded reflection request:"
msgstr "启用反思后，ZeroClaw 会改为请求代理已配置的模型提供方，从执行的一个**有界**片段（任务、工具调用轨迹和最终答案）中合成一个规范的 [`SKILL.md`](#create-a-markdown-skill)。每个输入都会独立截断到配置的字符预算，因此即使执行规模很大，也绝不会生成无限制的反思请求："

#: src/channels/git.md
msgid "With the GitHub provider, ZeroClaw authenticates as a **GitHub App** and replies as the app's own bot identity (`your-app[bot]`), so it works on any repository the app is installed on. There is no personal access token and no shared user account."
msgstr "使用 GitHub 提供方时，ZeroClaw 会以 **GitHub App** 身份进行认证，并以该应用自己的机器人身份（`your-app[bot]`）回复，因此它可在安装了该应用的任何仓库中工作。没有个人访问令牌，也没有共享用户账户。"

#: src/channels/git.md
msgid "With the Gitea/Forgejo provider, ZeroClaw authenticates with a personal access token against the instance's Gitea-compatible API and replies as the token owner."
msgstr "使用 Gitea/Forgejo 提供程序时，ZeroClaw 会使用个人访问令牌针对实例的 Gitea 兼容 API 进行身份验证，并以该令牌的所有者身份进行回复。"

