#: src/sop/observability.md
msgid "`/metrics` exposes observer metrics when `[observability] backend = \"prometheus\"`."
msgstr "当 `[observability] backend = \"prometheus\"` 时，`/metrics` 会暴露观测指标。"

#: src/ops/overview.md
msgid "`/metrics` returns Prometheus text exposition. It requires `[observability] backend = \"prometheus\"` in config; without it the endpoint returns a one-line \"backend not enabled\" hint."
msgstr "`/metrics` 返回 Prometheus 文本格式的指标数据。它需要在配置中设置 `[observability] backend = \"prometheus\"`；若未设置，该端点会返回一行 \"backend not enabled\" 提示。"

#: src/providers/routing.md
msgid "`/model <model-id>` selects a model within the active provider profile. If the value matches a `[[model_routes]]` hint or model, that route can switch both provider profile and model together."
msgstr "`/model <model-id>` 在当前激活的提供商配置文件中选择一个模型。如果该值匹配某个 `[[model_routes]]` 提示或模型，则该路由可以同时切换提供商配置文件和模型。"

#: src/providers/routing.md
msgid "`/models <type>.<alias>` selects the active provider profile for the sender session. Channel runtimes can also accept a bare `<type>` shorthand when exactly one configured alias exists for that provider family."
msgstr "`/models <type>.<alias>` 为发送方会话选择活动的提供方配置文件。当某个提供方系列恰好只配置了一个别名时，频道运行时还可接受裸 `<type>` 简写形式。"

