#: src/agents/history-management.md
msgid "`Agent::trim_history()` (`agent.rs`) applies an equivalent cap to structured `ConversationMessage` history in the ACP/gateway turn path, with additional orphan-safety cascades that avoid creating dangling `ToolResults` or `AssistantToolCalls` at the head after a drop."
msgstr "`Agent::trim_history()` (`agent.rs`) 在 ACP/gateway 回合路径中对结构化 `ConversationMessage` 历史应用了等效的上限，并附带额外的孤儿安全级联，避免在丢弃后在开头创建悬空的 `ToolResults` 或 `AssistantToolCalls`。"

