#: src/reference/config.md
msgid "`Forbidden` (the default) means a profile cannot delegate at all; `Allow` permits delegation. The set of reachable targets is _not_ an explicit allow-list — delegation is gated on the caller and target sharing a risk profile, so the shared profile determines who is reachable."
msgstr "`Forbidden`（默认）表示配置文件完全不能委派；`Allow` 允许委派。可达目标集合 _不是_ 显式的允许列表——委派由调用方和目标共享同一风险配置文件来限制，因此共享配置文件决定了哪些目标可达。"

