#: src/hardware/aardvark.md
msgid ""
"```\n"
"┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n"
"│                        STARTUP (boot)                        │\n"
"│                                                              │\n"
"│  1. Ask aardvark-sys: \"any adapters plugged in?\"             │\n"
"│  2. For each one found → register a device + transport       │\n"
"│  3. Load tools only if hardware was found                    │\n"
"└──────────────────────────────────────────┬───────────────────┘\n"
"                                           │\n"
"                    ┌──────────────────────▼───────────────────────┐\n"
"                    │              RUNTIME (agent loop)            │\n"
"                    │                                              │\n"
"                    │  User: \"scan i2c bus\"                        │\n"
"                    │     → agent calls i2c_scan tool              │\n"
"                    │     → tool builds a ZcCommand                │\n"
"                    │     → AardvarkTransport sends to hardware    │\n"
"                    │     → response flows back as text            │\n"
"                    └──────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n"
"```"
msgstr ""
"┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n"
"│                        启动（boot）                          │\n"
"│                                                              │\n"
"│  1. 询问 aardvark-sys：\"有任何适配器接入吗？\"               │\n"
"│  2. 对找到的每一个 → 注册一个设备 + 传输层                   │\n"
"│  3. 仅在检测到硬件时才加载工具                               │\n"
"└──────────────────────────────────────────┬───────────────────┘\n"
"                                           │\n"
"                    ┌──────────────────────▼───────────────────────┐\n"
"                    │              运行时（智能体循环）            │\n"
"                    │                                              │\n"
"                    │  用户：\"scan i2c bus\"                       │\n"
"                    │     → 智能体调用 i2c_scan 工具               │\n"
"                    │     → 工具构建一个 ZcCommand                 │\n"
"                    │     → AardvarkTransport 发送到硬件           │\n"
"                    │     → 响应以文本形式回传                     │\n"
"                    └──────────────────────────────────────────────┘"

