#: src/maintainers/labels.md
msgid "`agent:prompt` is for provider-visible prompt, context, and response-guidance policy. Use it when the work is about system-prompt content, tool-call formatting guidance, prompt-cache-sensitive context, channel response guidance, or other model-visible instruction surfaces that cross the base `agent`, `channel`, `memory`, `provider`, or `runtime` labels. Apply it in addition to applicable base or scope labels; it does not replace them. Do not apply it to every `crates/zeroclaw-runtime/src/agent/**` change; use the base `agent` label for ordinary agent runtime changes."
