msgid "`cargo web gen-api` renders the OpenAPI spec in-process from `zeroclaw_gateway::openapi::build_spec()`, writes it to `target/openapi.json`, and feeds that file to `openapi-typescript`. The same `build_spec()` serves `/api/openapi.json` at runtime, so `build_spec()` is the single contract source and the generated files are rebuilt on demand."
