msgid "`history::trim_history(history, max_history)` operates on the interactive (`ChatMessage`) history in `loop_.rs`. It preserves the system prompt, the first user message (the framing anchor that prevents silent-amnesia bugs), and the most recent `max_history` messages, dropping from the middle when the ceiling is exceeded."
