#: src/tools/mcp.md
msgid "`mcp.deferred_loading` is `false` by default, so configured MCP tools are included in the model context eagerly. Set it to `true` to place only MCP tool **names** in the system prompt; the LLM calls the built-in `tool_search` tool to fetch a tool's full schema before invoking it. This keeps the initial context window small when a server exposes many tools."
msgstr "`mcp.deferred_loading` 默认为 `false`，因此已配置的 MCP 工具会被预先加载到模型上下文中。将其设置为 `true` 可仅将 MCP 工具的**名称**放入系统提示词中；LLM 会在调用工具前先调用内置的 `tool_search` 工具来获取该工具的完整 schema。当服务器暴露大量工具时，这能保持初始上下文窗口较小。"

#: src/reference/cli.md
msgid "`mcp.servers` — Individual Model Context Protocol servers. Each entry binds a transport (stdio, http, sse), the command or URL to reach it, optional headers, and a `tool_timeout_secs` cap (≤ 600). Each server's `name` is its addressable key — rename via the section page rather than editing the field directly. Group servers into bundles under `mcp_bundles` below"
msgstr "`mcp.servers` — 单个 Model Context Protocol 服务器。每个条目会绑定一个传输方式（stdio、http、sse）、用于连接它的命令或 URL、可选请求头，以及 `tool_timeout_secs` 上限（≤ 600）。每个服务器的 `name` 是其可寻址键——请通过该分节页面重命名，而不是直接编辑该字段。将服务器分组到下面的 `mcp_bundles` 中。"

#: src/reference/config.md
msgid "`mcp_bundles.<alias>`"
msgstr "`mcp_bundles.<alias>`"

#: src/reference/config.md
msgid "`mcp_bundles`"
msgstr "`mcp_bundles`"

#: src/reference/cli.md
msgid "`mcp_bundles` — Named bundles of MCP servers, granted to agents that list the bundle in their `mcp_bundles`. Secure by default: an agent gets only the servers its bundles grant; with no bundle it gets no MCP servers"
msgstr "`mcp_bundles` — MCP 服务器的命名捆绑包，授予在其 `mcp_bundles` 中列出该捆绑包的代理。默认安全：代理只会获得其捆绑包所授予的服务器；如果没有捆绑包，则不会获得任何 MCP 服务器"

#: src/maintainers/labels.md
