#: src/tools/mcp.md
msgid "`mcp_prompts`: `action: \"list\"` lists prompts; `action: \"get\"` with `name` (prefixed `<server>__<name>`) and optional `arguments` returns the rendered prompt messages."
msgstr "`mcp_prompts`: `action: \"list\"` 列出提示；`action: \"get\"` 携带 `name`（前缀为 `<server>__<name>`）和可选的 `arguments` 时，返回渲染后的提示消息。"

#: src/tools/mcp.md
msgid "`mcp_resources`: `action: \"list\"` (optional `server`, `cursor`) lists resources; `action: \"read\"` with `uri` (prefixed `<server>__<uri>`) returns contents."
msgstr "`mcp_resources`: `action: \"list\"`（可选 `server`、`cursor`）列出资源；带 `uri`（前缀为 `<server>__<uri>`）的 `action: \"read\"` 返回内容。"

