#: src/architecture/decisions/ADR-009-wit-wasmtime-plugin-execution.md
msgid "`plugins-wasm-cranelift` enables Cranelift compilation where supported."
msgstr "`plugins-wasm-cranelift` 在受支持的平台上启用 Cranelift 编译。"

#: src/foundations/fnd-001-intentional-architecture.md
msgid "`plugins-wasm-pulley`"
msgstr "`plugins-wasm-pulley`"

#: src/architecture/decisions/ADR-009-wit-wasmtime-plugin-execution.md
msgid "`plugins-wasm-pulley` enables the Pulley interpreter for targets where Cranelift is unavailable or undesirable."
msgstr "`plugins-wasm-pulley` 为 Cranelift 不可用或不适用的目标启用 Pulley 解释器。"

#: src/developing/plugin-protocol.md
msgid "`plugins-wasm-pulley` is the most portable, supporting compilation on targets Cranelift does not cover."
msgstr "`plugins-wasm-pulley` 是最具可移植性的，支持在 Cranelift 不支持的目标上编译。"

#: src/architecture/decisions/ADR-009-wit-wasmtime-plugin-execution.md
msgid "`plugins-wasm-runtime-only` enables the smallest runtime-only host."
msgstr "`plugins-wasm-runtime-only` 启用最小的仅运行时主机。"

#: src/developing/plugin-protocol.md
msgid "`plugins-wasm-runtime-only` is the smallest and fastest to start: no JIT, so components are deserialized from a precompiled `.cwasm`."
msgstr "`plugins-wasm-runtime-only` 是最小且启动最快的：没有 JIT，因此组件会从预编译的 `.cwasm` 反序列化。"

#: src/foundations/fnd-001-intentional-architecture.md
msgid "`plugins-wasm`"
msgstr "`plugins-wasm`"

#: src/architecture/decisions/ADR-009-wit-wasmtime-plugin-execution.md
msgid "`plugins-wasm` enables the plugin host surface in the main workspace."
msgstr "`plugins-wasm` 可在主工作区中启用插件宿主表面。"

#: src/foundations/fnd-001-intentional-architecture.md
msgid "`plugins-wasm` is always-on, but it is not a single flag: it is a three-flag taxonomy. The host machinery is unconditional; the execution backend is a platform-level decision made at build time. `plugins-wasm` without a backend sub-flag does not produce a usable plugin runtime, because wasmtime needs either a compiler or an interpreter to execute a component."
msgstr "`plugins-wasm` 始终启用，但它不是一个单独的标志：它是一个三标志分类。宿主机制是无条件的；执行后端则是一个在构建时做出的平台级决定。没有后端子标志的 `plugins-wasm` 不会生成可用的插件运行时，因为 wasmtime 需要编译器或解释器之一来执行组件。"

#: src/developing/plugin-protocol.md
msgid "`plugins-wasm` is the umbrella that pulls the plugin host and its runtime integration into the binary. It is **required**: the backend features below select an execution engine but do not imply the umbrella, so building with only a backend feature succeeds and silently yields a binary with no `plugin` subcommand. Always pass `plugins-wasm` plus your chosen backend, e.g. `--features plugins-wasm,plugins-wasm-cranelift`."
msgstr "`plugins-wasm` 是将插件宿主及其运行时集成拉入二进制文件的总开关。它是**必需**的：下面的后端特性只会选择一个执行引擎，但不会隐式包含这个总开关，因此只构建某个后端特性会成功，但会静默地产生一个没有 `plugin` 子命令的二进制文件。务必同时传入 `plugins-wasm` 和你选择的后端，例如 `--features plugins-wasm,plugins-wasm-cranelift`。"

#: src/foundations/fnd-001-intentional-architecture.md
msgid "`plugins-wasm`, `skill-creation`"
msgstr "`plugins-wasm`，`skill-creation`"

