#: src/plugins/index.md
msgid "a `Linker` with exactly the imports its world and permissions call for: `logging` always, `inbound` for channels, `wasi:http` only when the manifest grants `http_client`. The HTTP context and the linked interface are derived from the same permission set and cross-checked at instantiation (`ensure_http_coherent`), so they cannot disagree."
msgstr "一个 `Linker`，其导入项严格对应其世界和权限所需：始终包含 `logging`，在通道场景下包含 `inbound`，仅当清单授予 `http_client` 时才包含 `wasi:http`。HTTP 上下文和链接接口都由同一权限集派生，并在实例化时进行交叉检查（`ensure_http_coherent`），因此它们不可能不一致。"

