#: src/zerocode/running.md
msgid "zerocode finds the daemon's local endpoint automatically: `<data_dir>/data/daemon.sock` on Unix, `\\\\.\\pipe\\zeroclaw-<hash>` on Windows. If the daemon isn't running, zerocode spawns an ephemeral one."
